4. 否定旧有错误理论
本体系彻底摒弃传统波动理论的核心错误假设：
不存在光波这一虚构的波动形式，光的传播本质是光子实体的集体运动；
明暗条纹的形成不存在波峰波谷能量抵消，路径禁区并非能量消失，而是光子群体能量包无法覆盖的空白区域；
否定波粒二象性的错误拟合，所有光学现象均可通过光子实体、能量包及群体运动规律完整解释，无需引入波动类概念。
5. 全篇总结定论
光的所有传播、干涉与衍射现象，均是物质粒子（光子）集体运动的宏观表现。核心逻辑闭环为：光子实体为基础→能量包为其能量作用范围→大量光子集体形成能量包间距→环境诱导触发路径分裂与衍射（重新分配 + 放大）
→能量包密集覆盖区为亮纹、路径禁区为暗纹。该体系完全基于客观实物运动规律，剔除所有虚构波动概念，实现了光学现象的实物化、简洁化解释，与传统波动理论的错误假设彻底切割。
Photon: The photon is an objectively real microscopic entity, the basic material unit composing light, with independent motion properties.
Energy Packet: The energy packet exists attached to the photon and refers to the energy action coverage formed by the photon during its spatial motion; this action range is variable in form, capable of compression and expansion, and is not an independent material particle.
Energy Packet Spacing: A single photon has no fixed constrained spacing. The energy packet spacing is an overall arrangement interval rule spontaneously formed when a large number of photons move collectively and synchronously. This spacing can be artificially adjusted and compressed, with no insurmountable fixed limit.
Path Forbidden Zone: Under constrained environments such as double slits, a large number of photons move uniformly according to the arrangement rules of the collective energy packets. Restricted by the overall interval arrangement, some spatial regions cannot be covered by the action range of the energy packets. Such blank regions that cannot be reached and have no energy coverage are defined as path forbidden zones, corresponding to the dark fringes observed in experiments.
Path Splitting: When a large number of photons move collectively, affected by the surrounding environment, boundaries and obstacles, they will spontaneously complete the redistribution of motion trajectories, and simultaneously generate diffusion motion from the outside to the inside, naturally forming multiple independent traveling paths. This characteristic is an inherent motion mode of photons themselves.
Diffraction: The essence of diffraction is that boundary conditions such as obstacles and slits redistribute and amplify the original motion paths of photons, further extending the diffusion range of the photon group and making the path differentiation effect more obvious.
Inherent multi-path motion of photons → Path redistribution and amplification when encountering obstacles → The collective energy packets form a stable arrangement spacing → The regions densely covered by energy packets are bright fringes, and the blank regions that cannot be covered are path forbidden zones, ultimately forming bright and dark fringes.
I. Supplementary: Clear Definition of Bright Fringes
A bright fringe region is a spatial area where energy packets are densely gathered and extensively overlapped when a large number of photons move collectively. There is no wave superposition at all; it is only the large number and dense arrangement of energy packets that form a visible bright area to the naked eye.
II. Supplementary: Complete Negation of the Core of the Old Theory
There are no light waves, wave-particle duality, or wave superposition and cancellation; dark fringes are absolutely not the result of energy disappearance or positive-negative cancellation; all interference and diffraction phenomena can be completely explained by only four points: photon entity + compressible energy packet + collective arrangement spacing + path forbidden zone.
III. Supplementary: Series Connection of the Entire Logic (used as a transition paragraph)
All propagation and fringe phenomena of light have the real existing photon as the underlying carrier, the compressible and deformable energy packet action range as the external performance, the collective spacing rules of a large number of photons as the macroscopic arrangement, and the difference between bright and dark originates from whether the energy packet covers the area or not. The blank uncovered areas are path forbidden zones (dark), and the densely covered areas are energy aggregation zones (bright).
Negation of the Old Erroneous Theory
This system completely abandons the core erroneous assumptions of the traditional wave theory: there is no fictional wave form such as light waves; the essence of light propagation is the collective motion of photon entities; the formation of bright and dark fringes does not involve energy cancellation of wave crests and troughs; path forbidden zones are not energy disappearance, but blank regions that cannot be covered by the collective energy packets of photons; the erroneous fitting of wave-particle duality is negated; all optical phenomena can be completely explained through photon entities, energy packets and the laws of collective motion, without introducing wave-related concepts.
Summary and Conclusion of the Entire Text
All propagation, interference and diffraction phenomena of light are macroscopic manifestations of the collective motion of material particles (photons). The core logical closed loop is: photon entity as the foundation → energy packet as its energy action range → a large number of photons collectively form energy packet spacing → environment-induced path splitting and diffraction (redistribution + amplification) → regions densely covered by energy packets are bright fringes, and path forbidden zones are dark fringes. This system is completely based on the laws of objective material motion, eliminates all fictional wave concepts, realizes a materialized and simplified explanation of optical phenomena, and completely cuts off from the erroneous assumptions of the traditional wave theory.
